<i>postpositional particle</i>: 라 [] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>postpositional particle</i><br>
<dt>라 []</dt><br>
<dd>ra</dd><br>
<dd>앞의 말이 원래 말해진 그대로 인용됨을 나타내는 조사.</dd><br>
<dd>A postpositional particle used to indicate that the preceding statement was a quote.</dd><br>
